You are part of something that is very hard to understand and wrap your head around - part of something bigger and together we are one. Accept all perspectives that cross your path and allow them to grow in your mind, you will feel peace and your mind will be at ease when you understand that you may never understand this unpredictable yet very beautiful journey we are on.
